text: Idrisovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Alkinsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 151 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Maloyaz, 7 km from Alkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Idrisovo, Salavatsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
